data.description:
Welcome to this charming, fully renovated home nestled in a picturesque neighborhood featuring stunning mountain views. Located within walking distance to the highly sought-after Kennedy Elementary School, this conveniently situated property offers not only a comfortable living space but also an unbeatable location for families.
With a total of three bedrooms and 1082 square feet, this home provides an ideal layout for both relaxation and functionality. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior that seamlessly blends modern upgrades with classic charm. The living and dining area creates a welcoming atmosphere, infused with an abundance of natural light that highlights the home's elegant finishes.
Unwind and rejuvenate in the spacious master bedroom, featuring tile floors, ample closet space, and windows that fill the room with sunlight. Two additional bedrooms provide versatile space for a home office, playroom, or guest accommodations, ensuring everyone has their own privacy.
This home doesn't stop impressing with its interior delights; the exterior offers just as much, if not more. Step outside to your private oasis, where the backyard beckons for evening barbecues, morning coffee, or simply basking in tranquility. The harmonious blend of greenery and mountain views from the street creates an idyllic backdrop for outdoor entertaining or relaxation.
Situated in a family-friendly neighborhood, the location of this home is truly unbeatable. Enjoy the quiet while being mere minutes away from the bustling downtown area, shops, restaurants, and entertainment options.
Don't miss this opportunity to own a fully renovated home in the highly desirable neighborhood, just a stone's throw away from Kennedy Elementary School. Schedule your showing today and make this beautiful home yours!
